No. 11-277. Ohio, Petitioner v. D.B. 565 U.S. 1100, 132 S. Ct. 846,

181 L. Ed. 2d 563,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8866. December 12, 2011.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris granted. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the Supreme Court of Ohio denied.

Same case below, 129 Ohio St. 3d 104, 950 N.E.2d 528.
